  <h1>Double Plate</h1>
  <h3>Source</h3>
  <text>
    <style color="0xaaaaaa" italic="true">Note: this page is ported from MCMOD's GTCEu wiki. <br></br>Author: <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/119280/">Oganesson897</style>, <br></br> <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" underlined="true" url-link="https://github.com/blackdragon2447">BlackDragon2447</style> <br></br></style>
  </text>
  <text>The main use for double plates is in the creation of <style color="0xbbffaa">Huge Pipes</style> and <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/turbine_blade" underlined="true">Turbine Blades</style> although not all <style color="0xbbffaa">Double Plates</style> can be used for both or even either, <style color="0xbbffaa">Double Plates</style> also show up in the crafting of cells and other various items.</text>
  <h3>Crafting</h3>
  <text>Double plates are created either manually by hammering two plates together or from from two plates or ingots in a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/bender" underlined="true">Bender</style>.</text>
